{"tid":2363223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"平安夜和你shop 學生判囚六個月","createTime":"2021-01-12T05:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:25:02.000Z","uid":10540,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f71e077d57be6b976cd069e29d45609f5d19e7e8","tid":2363223,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:09:20.000Z","msg":"案情指，前年平安夜，被告在尖沙咀海港城三樓拒抗三名便衣警員，警員報稱在拘捕疑犯期間，額頭、拇指等受傷，被告抗辯時稱遭制服後被警員扑頭。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉啓亮早前裁定被告罪成，認為三名警員都是誠實可靠，他今日判刑時指，案件發生不足一分鐘，雙方也有受傷，考慮到被告抗拒程度、年紀及沒案底，三項控罪合共判囚六個月。被告就定罪及刑期上訴，裁判官批准被告以一萬元現金擔保。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=419952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419952&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJufcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=3d616e27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419952&h=833468fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=419952</a>"},{"pid":"75f464f7e0ff92804c18766cab3304cd2d0d95a0","tid":2363223,"uid":307619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"上水企圖謀殺都有得保釋"},{"pid":"26a5151589ad545223428b4dfa0dfddb8a32f4e4","tid":2363223,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母刑期通脹到6個月已經覺得叫輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b68f91f9e537c5c3ff98bdec20d72958b653ce6","tid":2363223,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d066b0488df69f323c63ebbc15ca06f0ad69f106","tid":2363223,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"誠實可靠"},{"pid":"544388167bbc4311939646d7311b0459b0513b12","tid":2363223,"uid":16775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"其實告佢個樣係不配合強姦罪<img src=\"/